text.tspan: ArcanisHD is a mid 2.0 male scratcher.
He is an animator known for making
satire projects as well as a game developer
who makes amazing story driven games.
Arcanis is well known in the scratch
community and is favored by many for his
effort and is one of the top 200 scratchers.
